14:50.290 --> 14:51.359
BACK THERE.

14:51.360 --> 14:52.315
>> I COVER IT EVERY DAY

14:52.320 --> 14:54.254
WITH MAKEUP. IVE HAD SO MUCH

14:54.260 --> 14:55.409
SHAME SURROUNDING IT,

14:55.420 --> 14:56.284
I HAVENT EVEN BEEN ABLE

14:56.290 --> 14:57.279
TO BRING MYSELF TO SHOW IT

14:57.290 --> 14:59.053
TO A DOCTOR SO THAT

14:59.060 --> 15:01.528
I CAN HAVE IT TAKEN OFF.

15:01.530 --> 15:06.092
>> AND YET HERE YOU ARE.

15:06.100 --> 15:08.523
>> I SPEND MONTHS, SOMETIMES

15:08.530 --> 15:10.031
YEARS, WITH PEOPLE TRYING

15:10.040 --> 15:11.302
TO CHANGE THEIR BEHAVIOR

15:11.310 --> 15:16.031
IN THERAPY.

15:16.040 --> 15:19.032
GOD KNOWS I THOUGHT ID CHANGED.

15:19.040 --> 15:20.382
BUT THE TRUTH IS, NOTHING

15:20.390 --> 15:22.381
EVER REALLY HAPPENS UNLESS

15:22.390 --> 15:24.187
YOU TAKE ACTION IN YOUR LIFE,

15:24.190 --> 15:25.384
AND I WAS HOPING THAT YOU

15:25.390 --> 15:28.143
WOULD HELP ME DO THAT.

15:28.150 --> 15:31.597
>> HOWS TOMORROW SOUND?

15:31.600 --> 15:35.297
>> [SIGHS]

15:41.370 --> 15:43.065
>> JULES?

15:43.070 --> 15:44.503
I GOT CHINESE FOR DINNER.

15:44.510 --> 15:50.039
>> DID YOU GET ENOUGH FOR 3?

15:50.050 --> 15:52.644
SEAN, YOU REMEMBER MONICA.

15:52.650 --> 15:57.212
>> HELLO, DR. MCNAMARA.

15:57.220 --> 15:59.415
> > HELLO, MONICA.

15:59.420 --> 16:00.352
>> GUESS WHAT I FOUND OUT

16:00.360 --> 16:03.420
THIS MORNING.

16:03.430 --> 16:06.251
MARLOW HAS A STOMACH VIRUS.

16:06.260 --> 16:08.228
HE THREW UP ALL OVER THE HOUSE.

16:08.230 --> 16:10.061
I TOOK HIM TO THE EMERGENCY

16:10.070 --> 16:11.492
ROOM AND THE DOCTOR SAID THAT

16:11.500 --> 16:12.592
HE CANT BE AROUND CONNOR

16:12.600 --> 16:13.567
FOR A WEEK.

16:13.570 --> 16:15.367
>> THATS TERRIBLE.

16:15.370 --> 16:16.359
>> WHICH MEANT NO NANNY,

16:16.370 --> 16:18.429
SO I CALLED MONICA TO SEE

16:18.440 --> 16:20.101
IF SHE COULD REFER SOMEONE,

16:20.110 --> 16:21.042
AND SHE SAID THAT SHE WAS

16:21.050 --> 16:22.369
STILL IN TOWN AND SHED BE

16:22.380 --> 16:24.575
HAPPY TO FILL IN.

16:24.580 --> 16:26.639
>> REALLY?

16:26.650 --> 16:28.106
>> I THOUGHT THIS WAY,

16:28.110 --> 16:29.202
IF IT WORKS OUT, THEN WE DONT

16:29.210 --> 16:31.053
HAVE TO CANCEL THE HONEYMOON.

16:31.060 --> 16:32.049
[CONNOR CRYING]

16:32.060 --> 16:33.413
AH, HE JUST WOKE UP.

16:33.420 --> 16:36.412
ILL GET HIM. HI, SWEETIE.

16:41.070 --> 16:42.025
>> WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU

16:42.030 --> 16:43.065
TRYING TO DO?

16:43.070 --> 16:43.627
>> NOTHING.

16:43.630 --> 16:45.063
SHE CALLED ME. SHE SOUNDED

16:45.070 --> 16:46.389
SO DESPERATE, I WANTED TO HELP.

16:46.400 --> 16:47.321
>> WELL, YOURE NOT GONNA

16:47.330 --> 16:48.126
STAY IN THIS HOUSE

16:48.130 --> 16:48.994
AND TAKE CARE OF MY SON.

16:49.000 --> 16:50.206
>> WELL, IF I SAY NO NOW,

16:50.210 --> 16:51.404
WOULDNT SHE GET SUSPICIOUS?

16:52.540 --> 16:53.529
SAY YES IN THE FIRST PLACE?

16:53.540 --> 16:54.472
>> I NEEDED THE MONEY.

16:54.480 --> 16:56.573
I HAVENT FOUND ANY WORK YET.

16:56.580 --> 16:58.207
>> NO.

16:58.210 --> 17:00.110
>> LOOK, DONT WORRY.

17:00.120 --> 17:02.247
I WILL BE COMPLETELY

17:02.250 --> 17:04.741
PROFESSIONAL THIS WEEK.

17:04.750 --> 17:08.083
OUR SECRET IS SAFE.

17:08.090 --> 17:09.284
HAVENT YOU LEARNED YOU CAN

17:09.290 --> 17:10.496
TRUST ME YET?

17:12.500 --> 17:17.494
OHH! HE IS SO HANDSOME.

17:17.500 --> 17:19.092
>> HES A LITTLE CRANKY

17:19.100 --> 17:21.307
WHEN HE FIRST GETS UP.

17:21.310 --> 17:22.504
>> CAN I HOLD HIM?

17:22.510 --> 17:26.765
>> SURE.

17:26.770 --> 17:29.102
>> HI THERE.

17:29.110 --> 17:32.318
>> I THINK HE LIKES YOU.

17:35.480 --> 17:37.744
WHAT A RELIEF I FOUND HER, HUH?

17:53.200 --> 17:54.428
[ TATTOO YOU BY THE ROLLING

17:54.440 --> 17:57.068
STONES PLAYING]

18:09.250 --> 18:11.115
>> DO IT, DO IT,

18:11.120 --> 18:15.079
DO IT, DO IT,

18:15.090 --> 18:19.811
DONT WANNA BE YOUR SLAVE

18:19.820 --> 18:21.196
>> ISNT YOUR PARTNER GOING

18:21.200 --> 18:22.189
TO JOIN US? I WAS HOPING

18:22.200 --> 18:23.292
TO MEET HIM.

18:23.300 --> 18:25.291
SEAN AND I DO A LOT MORE SOLO

18:25.300 --> 18:27.222
SURGERIES THESE DAYS.

18:27.230 --> 18:28.561
>> IS THAT A RECENT DECISION?

18:28.570 --> 18:30.379
>> EVER SINCE OUR FIRST SESSION.

18:30.380 --> 18:31.472
>> SO I TAKE IT YOU TOLD

18:31.480 --> 18:32.469
SEAN ABOUT YOUR FEELINGS

18:32.480 --> 18:35.278
FOR HIM, THEN?

18:35.280 --> 18:36.474
>> THE ANSWER TO YOUR QUESTION

18:36.480 --> 18:37.629
IS, NO, I DIDNT TELL HIM

18:37.640 --> 18:39.176
WHAT WE TALKED ABOUT. IM

18:39.180 --> 18:40.613
NOT GAY, SO ITS NOT AN ISSUE.

18:40.620 --> 18:41.689
>> SOUNDS LIKE YOURE

18:41.690 --> 18:44.443
CONFLICTED ABOUT SOMETHING.

18:44.450 --> 18:49.342
>> DONT WANNA BE YOUR SLAVE

18:49.350 --> 18:52.319
>> [SCOFFS]

18:52.330 --> 18:54.252
[SIGHS]

18:56.760 --> 18:59.320
[SIGHS]

19:01.240 --> 19:03.367
I HAD A DREAM THE OTHER NIGHT.

19:03.370 --> 19:06.567
SEAN AND I WERE...LOVERS.

19:06.570 --> 19:08.231
I SAID SOMETHING, HE FREAKED

19:08.240 --> 19:10.640
OUT AND HID IN THE CLOSET.

19:10.650 --> 19:13.915
I WENT IN AFTER HIM AND WOUND UP

19:13.920 --> 19:15.478
IN SURGERY. THERE HE WAS

19:15.480 --> 19:20.383
ON THE TABLE. NEXT THING I KNOW,

19:20.390 --> 19:23.257
HES DEAD. BUT THEN I WAKE UP

19:23.260 --> 19:25.751
AND HES IN BED NEXT TO ME.

19:25.760 --> 19:28.729
IN THE DREAM, NOT IN REALITY.

19:28.730 --> 19:30.391
>> JUST BECAUSE WE HAVE DREAMS

19:30.400 --> 19:31.936
WHERE WE CAN FLY, DOESNT MAKE

19:31.940 --> 19:36.536
US SUPERMAN, CHRISTIAN.

19:36.540 --> 19:37.495
>> THERE WAS ANOTHER PERSON

19:37.500 --> 19:42.676
IN THE DREAM. A WOMAN.

19:42.680 --> 19:44.500
>> SOMEONE YOU CARE ABOUT,

19:44.510 --> 19:45.442
PERHAPS?

19:45.450 --> 19:46.701
>> YES.

19:46.710 --> 19:48.405
>> AND YOUVE BEEN INTIMATE

19:48.410 --> 19:49.946
WITH THIS PERSON?

19:49.950 --> 19:51.554
>> DEFINITELY. I REALLY

19:51.560 --> 19:52.515
LIKE THIS PERSON,

19:52.520 --> 19:53.418
BUT ITS A RELATIONSHIP

19:53.420 --> 19:57.618
I NEED TO...KEEP SECRET.

19:57.620 --> 19:58.609
>> SEEMS LIKE YOUR DESIRE

19:58.620 --> 19:59.780
TO BE WITH THIS WOMAN IS BEING

19:59.790 --> 20:00.791
EXPRESSED THROUGH YOUR DREAM

20:00.800 --> 20:02.461
ABOUT SEAN.

20:02.470 --> 20:03.459
>> SO YOURE SAYING IF

20:03.470 --> 20:04.425
IM DREAMING ABOUT SPENDING MY

20:04.430 --> 20:05.419
LIFE WITH SEAN, I REALLY WANT

20:05.430 --> 20:07.193
TO SPEND MY LIFE WITH HER?

20:07.200 --> 20:09.395
>> IF YOU REALLY WANT TO EASE

20:09.400 --> 20:11.504
YOUR ANXIETY ABOUT ALL THIS,

20:11.510 --> 20:12.431
YOU NEED TO CONFRONT THE WOMAN

20:12.440 --> 20:14.635
YOU CARE ABOUT,

20:14.640 --> 20:16.301
TELL HER HOW YOU REALLY FEEL.

20:25.650 --> 20:28.619
>> THERE YOU ARE.

20:28.620 --> 20:29.985
IVE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU

20:29.990 --> 20:32.390
TO COME OUT OF SURGERY.

20:32.400 --> 20:33.992
>> RAN A LITTLE LONGER

20:34.000 --> 20:36.423
THAN I THOUGHT.

20:36.430 --> 20:38.295
>> FEELS LIKE WE HAVENT

20:38.300 --> 20:40.461
SEEN EACH OTHER IN DAYS.

20:40.470 --> 20:42.665
WE NEED SOME TIME TOGETHER.

20:42.670 --> 20:44.831
>> WELL, YOURE IN LUCK.

20:44.840 --> 20:46.262
MY 10 AM. CONSULT

20:46.270 --> 20:47.362
JUST RESCHEDULED.

20:47.370 --> 20:49.338
>> I KNOW. IM THE ONE

20:49.340 --> 20:51.513
WHO ASKED THEM TO COME LATER.

20:59.020 --> 21:01.682
I...THOUGHT YOU COULD MAKE ME

21:01.690 --> 21:04.022
COME...NOW, INSTEAD.

21:07.530 --> 21:08.679
>> SORRY, IM NOT INTERESTED

21:08.690 --> 21:11.033
IN SLOPPY SECONDS ANYMORE.

21:11.040 --> 21:13.031
>> BURT HASNT BEEN ABLE TO

21:13.040 --> 21:14.496
HAVE SEX WITH ME IN ALMOST

21:14.500 --> 21:16.536
6 MONTHS, CHRISTIAN.

21:16.540 --> 21:18.633
>> YESTERDAY IN YOUR OFFICE?

21:18.640 --> 21:21.746
>> HE TRIED, BUT THINGS

21:21.750 --> 21:23.706
WENT SOFT PRETTY FAST.

21:23.710 --> 21:24.642
>> AND NOW YOU WANT ME

21:24.650 --> 21:26.049
TO BE YOUR STAND-IN DICK.

21:29.950 --> 21:31.884
>> YOURE NOT JUST A STAND-IN,

21:31.890 --> 21:34.609
CHRISTIAN. YOU KNOW THAT.

21:34.620 --> 21:36.053
>> NO, IM LITERALLY SOMEONE

21:36.060 --> 21:37.288
YOU NEED TO LOCK IN A ROOM

21:37.290 --> 21:39.815
JUST SO YOU CAN HAVE AN ORGASM.

21:39.820 --> 21:42.027
I CANT KEEP GIVING YOU JUST

21:42.030 --> 21:45.295
A PART OF ME ANYMORE...

21:45.300 --> 21:47.666
AND NOT ALL OF ME.

21:47.670 --> 21:48.694
>> WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

21:48.700 --> 21:49.689
>> IM SAYING I KNOW YOURE

21:49.700 --> 21:50.871
NEVER GONNA LEAVE BURT, AND ITS

21:50.880 --> 21:52.734
PROBABLY FOR THE BEST.

21:52.740 --> 21:54.378
IF HE DID FIND OUT ABOUT US,

21:54.380 --> 21:56.029
WED LOSE THE PRACTICE,

21:56.040 --> 21:56.938
ID LOSE MY PARTNER,

21:56.940 --> 21:59.079
WED LOSE EACH OTHER ANYWAY.

21:59.080 --> 22:01.082
ITS OVER.

22:05.590 --> 22:06.887
>> YOURE RIGHT.

22:10.320 --> 22:13.756
WE PROBABLY SHOULD HAVE...

22:13.760 --> 22:18.026
STOPPED THIS A LONG TIME AGO.

22:18.030 --> 22:20.430
IM SORRY.

22:20.440 --> 22:21.839
>> YOURE NOT SORRY.

22:21.840 --> 22:24.104
YOU GOT EXACTLY WHAT YOU WANTED.

22:24.110 --> 22:24.963
YOU RE STILL MARRIED.

22:24.970 --> 22:25.800
YOURE STILL RICH.

22:25.810 --> 22:26.663
YOU STILL GOT TO SCREW THE

22:26.670 --> 22:28.729
GOOD-LOOKING HOTSHOT SURGEON.

22:28.740 --> 22:29.707
IM SURE YOULL MOVE ON

22:29.710 --> 22:30.711
TO SOMEONE ELSE NOW.

22:30.720 --> 22:31.971
>> YOU THINK ITS THAT EASY

22:31.980 --> 22:34.119
FOR ME? THAT I HAD IT

22:34.120 --> 22:36.873
ALL PLANNED OUT LIKE THIS?

22:36.880 --> 22:38.973
IM THE ONE WHOS TRAPPED NOW,

22:38.980 --> 22:41.084
NOT YOU.

22:44.860 --> 22:45.952
>> NEXT TIME YOU DECIDE

22:45.960 --> 22:48.383
TO RESCHEDULE A CLIENT,

22:48.390 --> 22:51.666
CHECK WITH ME FIRST.

23:01.010 --> 23:02.944
>> JUST A SEC.

23:06.610 --> 23:07.645
OH. OH, MY GOD,

23:07.650 --> 23:08.674
IM SO GLAD YOURE HERE.

23:08.680 --> 23:09.601
I WAS JUST THINKING

23:09.610 --> 23:13.057
I COULD USE A DOCTOR.

23:13.060 --> 23:14.049
>> WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

23:14.060 --> 23:15.049
>> SOMETHING IVE ALWAYS WANTED

23:15.060 --> 23:19.759
TO DO--PIERCE MY BELLYBUTTON.

23:21.900 --> 23:23.868
WANT TO DO THE HONORS?

23:23.870 --> 23:25.758
>> NO, I REALLY SHOULDNT STAY.

23:25.770 --> 23:28.091
UH, I COULDNT SAY ANYTHING

23:28.100 --> 23:30.159
EARLIER CAUSE JULIA WAS THERE,

23:30.170 --> 23:31.899
BUT AFTER HAVING TIME TO SLEEP

23:31.910 --> 23:34.902
ON IT, I JUST DONT THINK THAT--

23:34.910 --> 23:36.172
WAIT--YOURE GONNA HURT

23:36.180 --> 23:37.772
YOURSELF.

23:37.780 --> 23:41.045
[TRAIN HORN BLOWING]

23:43.190 --> 23:44.088
YOU HAVE TO STERILIZE

23:44.090 --> 23:45.182
THE AREA FIRST.

24:01.870 --> 24:03.007
>> I GUESS YOUVE DONE

24:03.010 --> 24:05.638
THIS BEFORE.

24:05.640 --> 24:08.200
>> NEEDLE.

24:08.210 --> 24:09.632
THE KEY IS TO DO THIS AS FAST

24:09.640 --> 24:10.675
AS POSSIBLE. DO YOU HAVE

24:10.680 --> 24:11.647
THE RING?

24:11.650 --> 24:13.117
>> YEP.

24:16.780 --> 24:18.611
>> CLOSE YOUR EYES.

24:18.620 --> 24:20.076
>> ARE YOU KIDDING?

24:20.080 --> 24:23.026
I FINALLY GET TO WATCH YOU WORK.

24:29.690 --> 24:31.089
[SIGHS]

24:39.170 --> 24:41.206
I DIDNT EVEN FEEL IT.

25:06.830 --> 25:07.865
>> NEXT TIME, YOU WONT

25:07.870 --> 25:11.499
NEED MY HELP.

25:11.510 --> 25:14.035
>> OH...

25:14.040 --> 25:16.031
YOURE PAYING ME IN ADVANCE?

25:16.040 --> 25:19.009
>> MORE LIKE A SEVERANCE.

25:23.590 --> 25:24.739
>> YOU DONT HAVE TO PAY ME OFF,

25:24.750 --> 25:27.014
SEAN. IM A BIG GIRL.

25:27.020 --> 25:28.180
I CAN TAKE CARE OF MYSELF.

25:28.190 --> 25:29.009
>> I HEARD WHAT YOU SAID

25:29.020 --> 25:30.282
ABOUT NOT FINDING WORK

25:30.290 --> 25:31.951
AND NEEDING MONEY.

25:31.960 --> 25:35.020
AND YOUVE BEEN VERY KIND...

25:35.030 --> 25:38.750
CONSIDERING THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

25:38.760 --> 25:40.808
I SHOULD GET GOING.

25:55.550 --> 25:57.074
NOT A TRACE OF IT ANYWHERE.

25:57.080 --> 25:58.069
>> THINK OF ALL THE MONEY

25:58.080 --> 26:02.551
YOULL SAVE ON MAKEUP.

26:02.560 --> 26:03.652
>> I WANT TO THANK YOU

26:03.660 --> 26:04.922
FOR ALL YOUR HELP.

26:04.930 --> 26:06.557
>> NO. THANK YOU.

26:06.560 --> 26:07.879
I TOOK YOUR ADVICE THE OTHER

26:07.890 --> 26:10.029
DAY. THE WOMAN IN MY DREAM--

26:10.030 --> 26:11.099
CALLED IT OFF.

26:11.100 --> 26:12.738
SHE WAS MARRIED, AND

26:12.740 --> 26:13.729
THAT COMPLICATED MORE THAN

26:13.740 --> 26:15.662
JUST MY PERSONAL LIFE.

26:15.670 --> 26:16.932
SHE AND HER HUSBAND OWN OUR

26:16.940 --> 26:18.965
BUSINESS.

26:18.970 --> 26:22.679
>> THATS GREAT.

26:22.680 --> 26:23.977
>> THEN WHY DO YOU LOOK

26:23.980 --> 26:26.642
LIKE I JUST KILLED YOUR DOG?

26:26.650 --> 26:29.073
>> I THOUGHT...

26:29.080 --> 26:30.616
NEVER MIND WHAT I THOUGHT.

26:30.620 --> 26:31.655
>> NO, NO, NO. YOURE

26:31.660 --> 26:35.312
MY PATIENT NOW. TELL ME.

26:35.320 --> 26:36.856
>> I THOUGHT THE WOMAN

26:36.860 --> 26:38.851
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT WAS ME.

26:38.860 --> 26:42.125
SILLY, RIGHT? YEAH, I KNOW.

26:42.130 --> 26:44.360
MY RADAR WAS OFF.

26:44.370 --> 26:45.689
I OVERANALYZED.

26:45.700 --> 26:48.362
BUT ITS SOMETHING SHRINKS DO.

26:48.370 --> 26:52.079
BUT THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING...

26:52.080 --> 26:54.378
AND...GOOD LUCK.

27:06.120 --> 27:08.315
[CONNOR CRYING]

27:08.320 --> 27:10.242
>> JULES?

27:18.000 --> 27:20.730
[CONNOR CRYING]

27:20.740 --> 27:22.332
>> HONEY?

27:22.340 --> 27:24.001
>> OH, ITS OK, I GOT HIM.

27:32.020 --> 27:35.069
[COOING]

27:35.080 --> 27:39.346
[GIGGLING]

27:39.350 --> 27:41.420
[SHUSHING]

27:43.990 --> 27:45.389
JULIA WAS RIGHT.

27:45.390 --> 27:47.051
HE GETS SO FUSSY WHEN

27:47.060 --> 27:49.824
HE WAKES UP. I THINK

27:49.830 --> 27:53.834
HE MIGHT BE TEETHING.

27:53.840 --> 27:57.139
OH, ITS OK. SHH--I GOT HIM.

27:57.140 --> 27:59.335
>> WHERE IS JULIA?

27:59.340 --> 28:01.706
>> SHES AT HER PILATES CLASS.

28:01.710 --> 28:02.449
I GUESS SHES STILL TRYING

28:02.450 --> 28:03.405
TO LOSE SOME OF THAT BABY

28:03.410 --> 28:06.049
WEIGHT. NOT THAT SHE HAS

28:06.050 --> 28:07.301
A STOMACH YOUD WANT TO SEE

28:07.310 --> 28:09.744
A BELLYBUTTON RING ON NOW.

28:09.750 --> 28:10.785
>> GIVE ME MY SON.

28:10.790 --> 28:11.916
>> HE JUST CALMED DOWN.

28:11.920 --> 28:13.456
I THOUGHT NO ONE WAS HOME,

28:13.460 --> 28:15.712
AND, UM, HE JUST KEPT

28:15.720 --> 28:17.859
REACHING FOR IT,

28:17.860 --> 28:19.782
AND I DIDNT WANT HIM TO CRY.

28:19.790 --> 28:22.964
IM NOT THAT INSENSITIVE.

28:22.970 --> 28:24.392
NO.

28:24.400 --> 28:25.765
>> HAND ME MY SON AND LEAVE,

28:25.770 --> 28:28.762
OR IM CALLING THE POLICE.

28:28.770 --> 28:29.759
>> AND ILL HAVE TO TELL

28:29.770 --> 28:31.101
THEM ABOUT THE AFFAIR,

28:31.110 --> 28:32.805
JULIA WILL FIND OUT,

28:32.810 --> 28:33.936
YOUR MARRIAGE IS OVER,

28:33.940 --> 28:34.929
THEN WHO DO YOU THINK IS

28:34.940 --> 28:37.977
REALLY GOING TO SUFFER? CONNOR!

28:37.980 --> 28:39.936
IM THE ONLY ONE WHOS DOING

28:39.940 --> 28:42.488
WHATS BEST FOR YOUR BABY,

28:42.490 --> 28:43.889
NOT YOU.

29:01.810 --> 29:03.505
>> GET THE HELL OUT. NOW!

29:10.070 --> 29:11.514
>> YOU TOOK ADVANTAGE OF ME,

29:11.520 --> 29:13.476
SEAN, AND JULIA NEEDS

29:13.480 --> 29:15.971
TO KNOW ABOUT THAT.

29:35.140 --> 29:36.129
>> YOU CAN QUIT IT WITH

29:36.140 --> 29:37.391
THE SILENT TREATMENT, SEAN.

29:37.400 --> 29:38.492
I GAVE MICHELLE THE BIG SPEECH.

29:38.500 --> 29:40.036
ITS OVER. WERE NOT GONNA

29:40.040 --> 29:43.043
LOSE OUR JOBS.

29:43.050 --> 29:44.540
>> SHES BREAST-FEEDING HIM.

29:44.550 --> 29:45.869
>> JULIA? WHATS SO SPECIAL

29:45.880 --> 29:46.904
ABOUT THAT?

29:46.910 --> 29:48.002
>> MONICA. I CAME HOME YESTERDAY

29:48.010 --> 29:49.102
AND CAUGHT HER WITH HER

29:49.110 --> 29:50.543
BREAST IN MY SONS MOUTH.

29:50.550 --> 29:51.551
>> WHAT THE HELLS SHE DOING

29:51.560 --> 29:52.481
IN YOUR HOUSE ANYWAY?

29:52.490 --> 29:53.479
I THOUGHT YOU FIRED HER.

29:53.490 --> 29:54.855
>> AND JULIA REHIRED HER

29:54.860 --> 29:56.509
TO WATCH CONNOR WHILE MARLOWS

29:56.520 --> 29:58.954
OUT SICK. I KICKED HER OUT,

29:58.960 --> 30:00.109
NOW SHES THREATENING

30:00.120 --> 30:01.428
TO TELL JULIA.

30:01.430 --> 30:03.523
>> HUH.

30:03.530 --> 30:05.168
[ZIPS, SIGHS]

30:05.170 --> 30:06.865
LET HER.

30:06.870 --> 30:07.495
SHE MIGHT AS WELL COP TO

30:07.500 --> 30:08.421
TH E KENN EDY ASSASSINATION

30:08.430 --> 30:09.465
WHILE SHES AT IT.

30:09.470 --> 30:10.903
TELL JULIA ABOUT THE PSYCHOTIC

30:10.910 --> 30:12.400
BREAST-FEEDING AND SHE WONT

30:12.410 --> 30:14.435
BELIEVE A WORD MONICA SAYS.

30:14.440 --> 30:19.503
THAT GIRL IS CLEARLY A NUT JOB.

30:19.510 --> 30:20.807
